{
  "lesson": "WC-03-02",
  "audioMaster": "training/module03-sales/WC-03-02-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 230.348,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Start on the Tickets list.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.388,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Every sale at the wash ends up here, one row per ticket,",
      "startS": 1.799,
      "endS": 3.682,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "with its location, total, status, and tender.",
      "startS": 3.984,
      "endS": 8.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Status is worth a glance on the way in: paid and washed, paid but not washed, or voided.",
      "startS": 8.737,
      "endS": 10.744,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "There are millions of tickets,",
      "startS": 11.127,
      "endS": 14.216,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "so you always filter down to the one you need before you open it.",
      "startS": 14.755,
      "endS": 19.375,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Click the row.",
      "startS": 19.841,
      "endS": 20.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "The ticket opens on its own page, and watch the address bar:",
      "startS": 21.243,
      "endS": 24.783,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "it picks up a ticket I-D on the end.",
      "startS": 25.133,
      "endS": 27.361,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "That means this page has a fixed web address.",
      "startS": 27.761,
      "endS": 30.35,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Copy it later and anyone you send it to lands on this exact ticket.",
      "startS": 30.682,
      "endS": 34.565,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Read the header first.",
      "startS": 35.04,
      "endS": 36.471,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "The ticket number is the title, with the I-D, the location, and the time it rang underneath.",
      "startS": 37.263,
      "endS": 42.674,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "That timestamp matters more than it looks:",
      "startS": 43.541,
      "endS": 45.865,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "it tells you which shift the sale fell in, which you'll need if a drawer doesn't balance.",
      "startS": 46.219,
      "endS": 50.598,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Confirm this is the transaction the caller means before you read a single number off it.",
      "startS": 51.343,
      "endS": 56.381,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Top-right, two buttons.",
      "startS": 56.855,
      "endS": 58.495,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Back to Tickets takes you home.",
      "startS": 58.946,
      "endS": 60.694,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "The red one is Refund, and we do not touch it.",
      "startS": 61.075,
      "endS": 64.046,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "On a real ticket a refund moves money,",
      "startS": 64.334,
      "endS": 69.628,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "so running the full refund flow is off the table today, and parked for a lesson of its own.",
      "startS": 69.845,
      "endS": 71.502,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Read the button, leave it alone.",
      "startS": 71.872,
      "endS": 73.592,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Under the header, four quick figures.",
      "startS": 74.07,
      "endS": 76.333,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Ticket total, payments, status, and payment type.",
      "startS": 77.025,
      "endS": 80.326,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "For most calls, that band answers the question before you open a single tab.",
      "startS": 81.18,
      "endS": 85.472,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "What was it, was it paid, and how.",
      "startS": 85.917,
      "endS": 86.576,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "A mismatch between total and payments is your first clue something is off.",
      "startS": 86.889,
      "endS": 93.479,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Now the tabs.",
      "startS": 93.92,
      "endS": 94.916,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Five of them: Main, Details, Payments, Refunds, and Notes.",
      "startS": 95.638,
      "endS": 96.297,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Main opens by default and carries the record itself.",
      "startS": 96.805,
      "endS": 100.752,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Details breaks the sale into line items, Payments lists every tender against it,",
      "startS": 101.976,
      "endS": 104.782,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "and Notes holds the ticket's notes.",
      "startS": 105.553,
      "endS": 107.914,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "We work Main and Refunds today.",
      "startS": 108.195,
      "endS": 115.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Main opens on Ticket Information.",
      "startS": 115.76,
      "endS": 117.291,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "The I-D, the ticket number, the date and time in,",
      "startS": 117.291,
      "endS": 120.583,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "the location, the status, and the payment type.",
      "startS": 120.583,
      "endS": 123.032,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "This is the group that proves you're looking at the right sale,",
      "startS": 123.032,
      "endS": 126.966,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "and the status here matches the one you saw in the list.",
      "startS": 126.966,
      "endS": 130.64,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "Next, Financial Summary.",
      "startS": 131.04,
      "endS": 132.673,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Total, taxes, tendered, change due, reversed, and house account.",
      "startS": 133.018,
      "endS": 134.229,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "When someone disputes a charge, you read the numbers straight off here.",
      "startS": 134.434,
      "endS": 137.628,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Reversed is the field to check first:",
      "startS": 137.978,
      "endS": 141.492,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "it tells you whether money already came back before you promise anything.",
      "startS": 141.711,
      "endS": 143.748,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "And house account tells you if a fleet or business paid instead of a card.",
      "startS": 144.099,
      "endS": 151.667,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Two more groups.",
      "startS": 152.08,
      "endS": 153.003,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Staff and Equipment names the cashier, the cashier terminal, the greeter terminal,",
      "startS": 153.428,
      "endS": 156.728,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "and the shift, so you can tie a ticket to a person, a register, and a drawer session.",
      "startS": 157.025,
      "endS": 158.99,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Customer and Vehicle names the customer, the vehicle, the plate, and the state,",
      "startS": 159.407,
      "endS": 163.221,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "which is how you match a ticket to a plate on a dispute.",
      "startS": 164.11,
      "endS": 171.383,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Open the Refunds tab.",
      "startS": 171.894,
      "endS": 173.16,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "A table of any refunds on this ticket:",
      "startS": 173.16,
      "endS": 176.399,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "refund I-D, amount, reason, who processed it, and its status.",
      "startS": 176.399,
      "endS": 179.764,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "On a clean ticket it simply says no refunds recorded.",
      "startS": 179.764,
      "endS": 183.594,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "When there is one, this is where you read the reason it was given,",
      "startS": 183.594,
      "endS": 188.483,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "who handled it, and whether it actually went through.",
      "startS": 188.483,
      "endS": 191.331,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "One thing to notice: what isn't here.",
      "startS": 191.837,
      "endS": 194.129,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "No Edit Ticket button, no add-refund control, and no ninety-day lock like the old system had.",
      "startS": 194.129,
      "endS": 199.848,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "The header Refund button is the only way in,",
      "startS": 199.848,
      "endS": 203.349,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "and whether you can finish one depends on your security level.",
      "startS": 203.349,
      "endS": 206.951,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Lower levels need approval first.",
      "startS": 206.951,
      "endS": 209.02,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "We cover the security side later.",
      "startS": 209.02,
      "endS": 211.28,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "Last, copy the address.",
      "startS": 211.733,
      "endS": 212.968,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "That ticket I-D on the end means the URL reopens this exact ticket.",
      "startS": 212.968,
      "endS": 217.601,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "Paste it into a support ticket",
      "startS": 217.601,
      "endS": 219.864,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "and the next technician opens the same transaction you were looking at,",
      "startS": 219.864,
      "endS": 223.569,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "instead of searching millions of rows for it.",
      "startS": 223.569,
      "endS": 226.039,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "Then Back to Tickets, and nothing on the ticket has changed.",
      "startS": 226.039,
      "endS": 229.876,
      "timing": "proportional"
    }
  ]
}